reviewText: I cant wait to get more of Margies dvds. These are great techniques to add to my practice to help save my hands.

I originally bought this for the Thai Herbal Ball application & even though the Thai Bodywork was on the same video, It only has 15 minutes of the Herbal Ball Application. Wish they would have more info on the video.
Great Transaction! Item came quickly and packaged well. Is exactly what I was looking for. May buy more in the future.
i had learned this technique in a class years ago and so to have this dvd to review, to pause, rewind etc. if fantastic.
